1. *Zatvoren* je bio u sobi kada je odjednom počela da prska voda iz cevi. (He was locked in the room when suddenly water started spraying from the pipe.)

2. Ona je nekoliko sati čekala da se *zatvori* vrata. (She waited for several hours for the door to close.)

3. Ona je *zatvorila* oči i pustila da joj misli odu u nedogled. (She closed her eyes and let her thoughts wander.)

4. Njegovo ponašanje je *zatvorilo* joj srce i nije mogla da mu oprosti. (His behavior closed her heart and she couldn't forgive him.)

5. Oni su *zatvorili* vrata kuće i otišli na putovanje. (They closed the doors of the house and went on a journey.)